<p>Using this line to install font in innosetup.</p>  <pre><code>Source: Executables\Tools\Fonts\password.TTF; DestDir: "{fonts}";    Flags: onlyifdoesntexist; FontInstall: "Password" </code></pre>  <p>I can see the files getting copied over to the <code>c:\windows\fonts</code> folder, but they are not registered under fonts. Basically they are getting copied but not installed.</p>